{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1573879, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "…？", "timestamp": 1619888058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为何一定要汉化？？？多民族当然要包容多语言啊", "timestamp": 1619888068, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#令人不适", "timestamp": 1619888107, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573900, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "......？什么鬼？#引战 #令人不适", "timestamp": 1619888178, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573906, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 本人新疆人少数民族，说本民族语言碍你那儿了？", "timestamp": 1619888196, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573909, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在中国是强大的，少数民族自然心向祖国；我担心的是，如果哪一天国家出现危机时，少数民族也有可能如五胡乱华一般，成为分裂国家的势力", "timestamp": 1619888209, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573923, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573909, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 说句难听的，如果一个国家这么防着少数民族，以至于要用文化灭绝的方式，那这个国家分裂了可能更好", "timestamp": 1619888272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573926, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573909, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 别扣帽子", "timestamp": 1619888293, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573930, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "国家有你这种汉族至上的思想才是危机", "timestamp": 1619888333, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573933, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "少数民族不配传承文化呗", "timestamp": 1619888363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573936, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "国家当然没有这么防着少数民族；然而，如果任由所有的少数民族，自己的民族认同过于强烈时，对比历史情况，很容易出现民族利益高于国家利益的情况", "timestamp": 1619888383, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573936, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不会，只要不压迫，平等对待，彼此信任就不会有这种情况出现，民族立场但不是单纯的极端民族主义", "timestamp": 1619888669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1573986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573936, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 怎么感觉你是我室友呢？", "timestamp": 1619888776, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573936, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我对你很失望", "timestamp": 1619889450, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "政治不正确，但思路没毛病", "timestamp": 1619890462, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "文化灭绝是吧？", "timestamp": 1619890999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574221, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574191, "tag": null, "text": "不想想怎么让少数民族真正发自内心地尊重与维护这个国家，反倒是一天到晚跟防贼一样防着人家搞分裂，甚至采用文化灭绝的极端方式，那只能说这样的国家的存在本身就是个问题", "timestamp": 1619891336, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574259, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "苏联一心想洗文化 最后还不是崩了", "timestamp": 1619891989, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574580, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我不认为统一语言文字有什么不好，确实也应该这样做。", "timestamp": 1619916837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573890, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 比利时两种语言，瑞士三种语言，只有索多玛才会像一条利维坦一样吞噬一切与己不同的事物。", "timestamp": 1619918435, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574684, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574646, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 美国呢？美国有几种语言？😅", "timestamp": 1619919227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574155, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 美国没有官方语言qqqxx", "timestamp": 1619919293, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574698, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574684, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 至少说西班牙语的一大堆", "timestamp": 1619919320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574703, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574698, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 这没什么，你去新疆看也是很多维语，西藏青海也是很多藏语，蒙语也一样。关键是你不能否认美国的绝对主流语言是英语，从来没见过甚么大学全部用西班牙语授课", "timestamp": 1619919486, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574698, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 不止大学，基础阶段的学校也没有吧", "timestamp": 1619919516, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1574711, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1574698, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 但是，新疆以前拿着不经过教育部审核的维语教材授课，在里面公然宣称疆独主义，这难道是可以容忍的吗？", "timestamp": 1619919586, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1577009, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "关键词：国家通用语言\n\n目前国家在大力推广汉语普通话（这是好的）\n顺便还在推广儒家、国学（？？？）", "timestamp": 1619950586, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1577014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": 1573909, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你怎么看待马来西亚华族现在的遭遇呢？", "timestamp": 1619950628, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1589680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1", "timestamp": 1620146589, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1612768, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 309625, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "2\n", "timestamp": 1620459505, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 309625, "reply": 30, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#一个疑问\n中国作为一个多民族国家，如何才能对少数民族汉化呢？\n看到新疆人还在说自己的语言，感到一丝丝担忧", "timestamp": 1619888037, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1620459507, "url": "", "vote": {}}}